<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:700px;"><img src="https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-cn-1239/breath.jpg" style="width:700px;" alt="breath.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:700px;">
<p><span class="hover2"><span style="width: 180px">SCP-CN-1239-2-A</span>SCP-CN-1239-2</span></p>
</div>
